Class NoMarkerLogging

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.event.NoMarkerLogging

  • public class NoMarkerLogging
extends java.lang.Object
    NoLogging is a MarkerLoggingAdapter that does absolutely nothing – no logging at all.
